== 典礼资讯 ==
[[File:Ellen_DeGeneres_2011.jpg|缩略图]]再度主持奥斯卡]]
学院不顾去年颁奖礼毁誉参半的评价，再次聘任尼尔·梅隆和克雷格·乍丹担任制片人<ref>{{cite news|last=Breznican|first=Anthony|title=Oscar Return: Craig Zadan and Neil Meron to produce show again|url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2013/04/16/oscar-sequel-craig-zadan-and-neil-meron-to-produce-show-again/|accessdate=2014-04-01|work=[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]|publisher=[[时代华纳|时代华纳]]|date=2013-04-16|archive-date=2013-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131109182718/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2013/04/16/oscar-sequel-craig-zadan-and-neil-meron-to-produce-show-again/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而，[[塞思·麦克法兰|塞思·麦克法兰]]宣布不再担任司仪，他在[[推特|推特]]发布声明：“批评声带来的打击，让我无法再次出席奥斯卡，尽管尝试依照日程表工作是明智的，但我真的要洗洗睡了<ref>{{cite news|last=Abramovitch|first=Seth|title=Seth MacFarlane Bows Out of Oscars|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/seth-macfarlane-bows-oscars-525605|accessdate=2014-04-01|work=[[好莱坞报道者|好莱坞报道者]]|publisher=Prometheus Global Media|date=2013-05-20|archive-date=2014-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140608235108/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/seth-macfarlane-bows-oscars-525605|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”此外，一个多月前曾与《[[周六夜现场|周六夜现场]]》同僚[[艾米·波勒|艾米·波勒]]共同主持[[第70届金球奖|第70届金球奖]]的喜剧演员[[蒂娜·菲|蒂娜·菲]]，接受《[[赫芬顿邮报|赫芬顿邮报]]》专栏作者麦克·莱恩专访时，表示会拒绝任何主持奥斯卡广播节目的提议并评论道：“我只觉得做这样的演出很辛苦，尤其对女性而言，有几个月都是在穿礼服中度过的——没辙<ref>{{cite news|last=Griffith|first=Janelle|title=Tina Fey says 'no way' to hosting the Oscars|url=http://www.nj.com/entertainment/index.ssf/2013/02/tina_fey_says_no_to_oscars.html|accessdate=2014-04-01|work=The Star-Ledger|publisher=Advance Publications|date=2013-02-27|archive-date=2014-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140417120323/http://www.nj.com/entertainment/index.ssf/2013/02/tina_fey_says_no_to_oscars.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

[[谢丽尔·布恩·艾萨克斯|谢丽尔·布恩·艾萨克斯]]当选[[美国电影艺术与科学学会|美国电影艺术与科学学会]]主席不久后，2013年8月，梅隆和乍丹正式宣布《[[艾伦秀|艾伦秀]]》主持人艾伦·德杰尼勒斯担任典礼司仪<ref>{{cite news|last=Lee|first=Chris|title=Ellen DeGeneres back to host 2014 Oscars|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2013/aug/02/entertainment/la-et-mn-ellen-degeneres-back-as-oscars-host-for-2014-20130802|accessdate=2014-04-01|work=Los Angeles Times|publisher=Tribune Company|date=2013-08-02|archive-date=2014-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140410121357/http://articles.latimes.com/2013/aug/02/entertainment/la-et-mn-ellen-degeneres-back-as-oscars-host-for-2014-20130802|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他们这样解释再次请回艾伦担任主持人的原因：“我们这对老朋友，一直想找一个能让我们共同合作的项目，想必没有什么能比携手呈现[[奥斯卡颁奖典礼|奥斯卡颁奖典礼]]更为精彩的了。如今没有多少明星的喜剧天赋、热情和人情味能与她比肩，她的粉丝无处不在。我们希望[[杜比剧院|杜比剧院]]和全球各地的家庭观众，听到这一消息感到兴奋<ref>{{cite news|last=Gennisq|first=Sadie|title=Ellen DeGeneres to Host the Oscars|url=http://www.tvguide.com/news/ellen-degeneres-host-oscars-2014-1068788.aspx|accessdate=2014-04-01|work=[[电视指南_(杂志)|电视指南]]|date=2013-08-02|archive-date=2014-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140417110547/http://www.tvguide.com/news/ellen-degeneres-host-oscars-2014-1068788.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”艾伦本人对此消息很高兴：“第二次主持奥斯卡了，当然高兴。照他们所说，看来拿第三次就要魅力了<ref>{{cite news|last=Carter|first=Bill|title=Ellen DeGeneres to Host Next Year’s Oscars|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/08/03/business/media/ellen-degeneres-to-host-next-years-oscars.html?_r=0|accessdate=2014-04-01|work=[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]|publisher=The New York Times Company|date=2013-08-02|archive-date=2014-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141017234353/http://www.nytimes.com/2013/08/03/business/media/ellen-degeneres-to-host-next-years-oscars.html?_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

按照去年的惯例，梅隆和乍丹给今年定的主题是“向荧屏英雄致敬”：“借致敬那些丰富了我们观影体验的英雄，我们希望营造一个充满欢乐的夜晚。其中包括那些承担风险，以挑衅性主题和大胆的角色冲击我们的演员和制片人们。他们都是荧屏英雄<ref>{{cite news|last=Gray|first=Tim|title=Oscars: Show to Focus on Movie Heroes|url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/oscars-show-to-focus-on-movie-heroes-1201055903/|accessdate=2014-04-02|work=Variety|publisher=PMC|date=2014-01-14|archive-date=2014-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140418064231/http://variety.com/2014/film/news/oscars-show-to-focus-on-movie-heroes-1201055903/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”为了回应主题，学院在[[贝弗利山庄|贝弗利山庄]]总部大堂举办举办“奥斯卡致敬电影英雄”的展览。展览精选共70部电影的海报、剧照和道具，包括剧本、漫画书和真实生活中的英雄<ref>{{cite news|last=Gettell|first=Oliver|title=Oscars to celebrate movie heroes at this year's ceremony|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/envelope/moviesnow/la-et-mn-oscars-movie-heroes-celebration-2014-ceremony-20140114,0,6833327.story#ixzz2z5BQp9cv|accessdate=2014-04-16|work=[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]|publisher=Tribune Company|date=2014-01-14|archive-date=2014-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140416233845/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/envelope/moviesnow/la-et-mn-oscars-movie-heroes-celebration-2014-ceremony-20140114%2C0%2C6833327.story#ixzz2z5BQp9cv|dead-url=no}}</ref>。“官方指定超级英雄”《[[超凡蜘蛛侠|超凡蜘蛛侠]]》主演[[安德鲁·加菲尔德|安德鲁·加菲尔德]]与5岁癌症康复者梅利·斯科特原订共同亮相展览，但这一环节因时间关系被取消<ref>{{cite news|last=Gettell|first=Oliver|title=Oscars: 'Batkid' appearance with Andrew Garfield cut at last minute|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/envelope/moviesnow/la-et-mn-oscars-batkid-appearance-with-andrew-garfield-cut-at-last-minute-20140306,0,1973863.story#axzz2v7nrtsG3|accessdate=2014-03-06|work=[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]|publisher=Tribune Company|date=2014-03-06|archive-date=2014-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140307004242/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/envelope/moviesnow/la-et-mn-oscars-batkid-appearance-with-andrew-garfield-cut-at-last-minute-20140306%2C0%2C1973863.story#axzz2v7nrtsG3|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。

其他人亦参与了节目的转播和推广。荣获[[托尼奖|托尼奖]]的艺术总监{{link-en|德里克·麦克莱恩|Derek McLane}}为演出设计了一套新的舞美<ref>{{cite news|title=Oscar Production Team Announced|url=http://www.deadline.com/2014/01/academy-announces-oscar-production-team/|accessdate=2014-03-05|work=Deadline Hollywood|publisher=PMC|date=2014-01-15|archive-date=2014-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140217192229/http://www.deadline.com/2014/01/academy-announces-oscar-production-team/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。制片人保罗·费戈制作了一分钟的典礼预告片，片中德杰尼勒斯与250名舞者同台献舞，对着摇滚乐队{{link-en|发脾气的菲兹|Fitz & the Tantrums}}的歌曲《{{link-en|浪行者|The Walker}}》的口型<ref>{{cite news|last=Hertzfield|first=Laura|title=Ellen DeGeneres and a sea of tuxes strut to Fitz & The Tantrums in new Oscar promo -- VIDEO|url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2013/12/19/ellen-degeneres-paul-feig-oscar-promos/|accessdate=2014-04-01|work=[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]|publisher=[[时代华纳|时代华纳]]|date=2013-12-19|archive-date=2014-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140220105319/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2013/12/19/ellen-degeneres-paul-feig-oscar-promos/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。典礼期间，[[查尼·泰坦|查尼·泰坦]]介绍了一支“奥斯卡之队”，由学院从全国高校中甄选的六名学生组成，在典礼中负责给颁奖嘉宾递奖杯<ref>{{cite news|last=Lewis|first=Hilary|title=Oscar College Contest Winners Announced|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscar-college-contest-winners-announced-677714|accessdate=2014-04-01|work=[[好莱坞报道者|好莱坞报道者]]|publisher=Prometheus Global Media|date=2014-02-06|archive-date=2014-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140404204316/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscar-college-contest-winners-announced-677714|dead-url=no}}</ref>。前[[美国小姐|美国小姐]]{{link-en|蕾切尔·史密斯|Rachel Smith}}将主持典礼官网幕后视频播客“探班奥斯卡<ref>{{cite news|last=Smith|first=Rachel|title=Oscar.com Goes Behind The Scenes Of Nominations With First Installment Of Exclusive Inside The Oscars Video Series|url=https://www.oscars.org/press/pressreleases/2014/20140115.html|accessdate=2014-04-16|work=[[美国电影艺术与科学学会|美国电影艺术与科学学会]]|publisher=AMPAS|date=2014-01-15|archive-date=2014-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140417083940/https://www.oscars.org/press/pressreleases/2014/20140115.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> ”。

