=== 专业评价 ===
典礼收到了毁誉参半的评价。一些媒体对表演很是挑剔。《[[匹兹堡邮报|匹兹堡邮报]]》电视评论家{{link-en|罗伯·欧文|Rob Owen (journalist)}}感叹：“德杰尼勒斯为周日的典礼带来可预见的体面，这跟指定赞助品牌比起来简直是败笔。”他还讽刺“致敬银幕英雄”短片过于耗时间，皆因奥斯卡剪辑向来如此<ref>{{cite news|last=Owen|first=Rob|title=Tuned In: Oscars dull despite DeGeneres|url=http://www.post-gazette.com/ae/tv-radio/2014/03/03/Oscars-dull-despite-DeGeneres/stories/201403030111|accessdate=2014-04-01|work=Pittsburgh Post-Gazette|publisher=Crain Communications|date=2014-03-03|archive-date=2014-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140303165252/http://www.post-gazette.com/ae/tv-radio/2014/03/03/Oscars-dull-despite-DeGeneres/stories/201403030111|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[Hitfix|Hitfix]]专栏作者{{link-en|艾伦·赛普威尔|Alan Sepinwall}}哀叹典礼“已黔驴技穷，所有乐趣被获奖者感言抢光。”他表示，德杰尼勒斯的许多绝技都失败收场，《[[绿野仙踪_(电影)|绿野仙踪]]》75周年献礼环节感觉太随便<ref>{{cite news|last=Sepinwall|first=Alan|title=Review: Pizzas, celebrity selfies and pointless montages at the 2014 Academy Awards|url=http://www.hitfix.com/whats-alan-watching/review-pizzas-celebrity-selfies-and-pointless-montages-at-the-2014-academy-awards|accessdate=2014-04-01|publisher=[[HitFix|HitFix]]|date=2014-03-02|archive-date=2014-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140409081250/http://www.hitfix.com/whats-alan-watching/review-pizzas-celebrity-selfies-and-pointless-montages-at-the-2014-academy-awards|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[好莱坞报道|好莱坞报道]]》的[[蒂姆·古德曼|蒂姆·古德曼]]则打趣：“差劲的导演和制片，口水不断，要么就是无聊，要么就是德杰尼勒斯畏首畏尾至少半个小时，似乎完全放弃的样子，搞得典礼华而不实。”他还指出，表演使用大量的短片铺垫和桥段，拖累转播的步伐<ref>{{cite news|last=Goodman|first=Tim|title=Oscars TV Review: Ellen Flops in Long, Boring, Self-Involved Show|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/oscars-tv-review-ellen-flops-685409|accessdate=2014-04-01|work=[[好莱坞报道者|好莱坞报道者]]|publisher=Prometheus Global Medua|date=2014-03-02|archive-date=2014-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140323092131/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/oscars-tv-review-ellen-flops-685409|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
   
其他媒体对转播的评价更为积极。《[[电视指南_(杂志)|电视指南]]》电视评论家马特·劳什，认为德杰尼勒斯“减轻奥斯卡必然会有的沉闷补丁以往给人的痛苦”，还盛赞数位演员和典礼的音乐<ref>{{cite news|last=Roush|first=Matt|title=Review: A Slice of Oscar History|url=http://www.tvguide.com/News/Oscar-Review-History-Ellen-DeGeneres-Selfie-1078738.aspx|accessdate=2014-03-05|work=[[电视指南_(杂志)|电视指南]]|publisher=[[CBS公司|CBS公司]]|date=2014-03-03|archive-date=2014-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140417111803/http://www.tvguide.com/News/Oscar-Review-History-Ellen-DeGeneres-Selfie-1078738.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[美联社|美联社]]的弗雷泽·摩尔称赞德杰尼勒斯的表现：“她似乎成为那晚无言的主题：让好莱坞时髦一族给观众以人性化。作为回报，巨星们展示出最好一面。”他总结：“总之，奥斯卡就是时尚秀，弹壳少，尴尬少，渐入渐出<ref>{{cite news|last=Moore |first=Frazier |title=Oscarcast: A fine scene hosted by Ellen DeGeneres |url=http://www.fortwayne.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20140303/ENT/320144503/1027 |accessdate=2014-04-16 |work=The News-Sentinel |publisher=Ogden Newspapers |date=2014-03-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140417084716/http://www.fortwayne.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20140303%2FENT%2F320144503%2F1027 |archivedate=2014-04-17 }}</ref>。”《[[每日野兽|每日野兽]]》娱乐编辑马洛·斯特恩表示：“德杰尼勒斯遵循最出色的典礼司仪[[比利·克里斯托|比利·克里斯托]]、[[蒂娜·菲|蒂娜·菲]]和[[艾米·波勒|艾米·波勒]]的步伐，顺应观众，与大腕有着过多的欢乐互动<ref>{{cite news|last=Stern|first=Marlow|title=Surprise! Ellen DeGeneres is the Best Oscars Host in a Decade|url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2014/03/03/ellen-degeneres-delivers-the-best-oscars-hosting-stint-in-a-decade.html|accessdate=2014-04-16|work=每日野兽|publisher=IAC|date=2014-03-03|archive-date=2014-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140409020818/http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2014/03/03/ellen-degeneres-delivers-the-best-oscars-hosting-stint-in-a-decade.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

