[[美国广播公司|美国广播公司]]在美国直播了典礼，全程平均吸引4372万人观看，较[[第85届奥斯卡金像奖|去年]]增长6%<ref>{{cite news|last=O'Connell|first=Michael|title=TV Ratings: Oscars Rise to 43.7 Million Viewers, Most-Watched in Over 10 Years|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/tv-ratings-oscars-rise-437-685337|accessdate=2014-03-05|work=[[好莱坞报道者|好莱坞报道者]]|publisher=Prometheus Global Media|date=2014-03-04|archive-date=2014-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140305053538/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/tv-ratings-oscars-rise-437-685337|dead-url=no}}</ref>。据估计，有7278万观众观看了所有或一部分奖项。有25.66%的家庭观看典礼，占总收视份额39.93%<ref>{{cite news|last=Golum|first=Rob|title=U.S. Broadcast Television Ratings for the Week Ended March 2|url=http://www.businessweek.com/news/2014-03-04/u-dot-s-dot-broadcast-television-ratings-for-the-week-ended-march-2|accessdate=2014-03-05|work=[[彭博商业周刊|彭博商业周刊]]|publisher=[[彭博新闻社|彭博新闻社]]|date=2014-03-04}}</ref>。此外，节目在18-49岁年龄段观众赢得了13.79%的较高收视率，占总收视份额34.52%<ref>{{cite news|last=Levin|first=Gary|title=Nielsen ratings: Academy Awards hands big win to ABC|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/tv/2014/03/04/nielsen-tv-weekly-ratings-highlights/6013087/|accessdate=2014-03-05|work=[[今日美国|今日美国]]|publisher=Gannett Company|date=2014-03-04|archive-date=2014-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140305012333/http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/tv/2014/03/04/nielsen-tv-weekly-ratings-highlights/6013087/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这是奥斯卡奖转播自2000年[[第72届奥斯卡金像奖|72届]]以来的最高收视率<ref>{{cite news|last=Boedeker|first=Hal|title=Oscars score best ratings in 14 years|url=http://www.orlandosentinel.com/entertainment/blogs/tv-guy/os-oscars-score-best-ratings-in-10-years-20140303,0,2547158.post|accessdate=2014-04-01|work=Orlando Sentinel|publisher=Tribune Company|date=2014-03-03|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140417120314/http://www.orlandosentinel.com/entertainment/blogs/tv-guy/os-oscars-score-best-ratings-in-10-years-20140303,0,2547158.post|archivedate=2014-04-17}}</ref>。

